      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the breathing thing for like 10 mins but its not really helping much. the pain is still there and it actually feels kinda weirdly localized to one side... like a stabbing sensation. but i really dont want to spend my vacation in a dubai hospital lol. do u think it could just be muscle strain from sitting in that cramped airplane seat for so long? that happens to me sometimes.",
